version_description: There are no tabs for this song. It is important for Ultimate Guitar to have lots of tabs at the use of users and it was disappointing to see that no one else had made a, "King of Love" tab. The goal from me, for this tab, is that others will be able to use it to better their Ultimate Guitar experience. (Also, the song CAN be played with no CAPO, but to add a twist, CAPO 1 could be useful.

Accurate and based off of the original studio recording. Proofread and able to be simplified for "acoustic versions." Primarily transcribed to enable easy transposition or use of multiple guitars both with and without capos.
